:{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31914,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/09\/hijab-women-blind-men\/","url_meta":{"origin":40616,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Women veiling themselves from men, even blind men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: While we were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, Ibn Maktum was given permission to enter. He entered and that was after the command to veil. The Prophet said, \u201cVeil yourselves from him.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is he not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/18\/perfume-of-men-and-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":40616,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Perfume: The perfume of men and women","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 18, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe perfume of men is that which scent is apparent and color is hidden. The perfume of women is that which scent is hidden and color is apparent.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2787 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/menses-missed-sawm-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":40616,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women make up missed fasts, not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen we were afflicted with menstruation, we were ordered to make up missed fasts but not missed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 335 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/17\/prohibition-describing-sex\/","url_meta":{"origin":40616,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Prohibition of verbally describing sexual features","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA woman should not touch another woman and then describe her figure to her husband as if he were gazing at her.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5240 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.